\cf2 \'93You are Magic man! Defender of America! For years you have kept this 		great country safe from all those who would try to harm it. Unfortunately, 		your enemies from years past have teamed up in an attempt to wreak havoc on 	those you swore to protect. They have been successful so far as they caught 		you off guard and have turned 50% of the population into frogs. What evil! 		Fortunately, there\'a0is still time to change them back but the clock is ticking. 		Due to the late start, you\'a0only have six minutes to transform the frogs back 		into people before they are stuck\'a0as frogs forever! Luckily, your enemies, 		Wiley Wizard and Professor Paranoia to\'a0name a few, are nothing if not good 		sports and realize the impossibility of your task.\'a0They guarantee that if you 		can save just ten people they will distribute an antidote\'a0all across the world 		that is capable of transforming the frogs back into people even\'a0after the spell 		becomes permanent. However, if you fail, they vow to condemn the rest\'a0of 		America to life as a frog for the rest of their days. The world\'92s fate rests in 		your hands. Good Luck.\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0
